title: De Sluizen van IJmuiden bijna 100 jaar geleden, in 1924, in kleur!

sources.title: De Oldify Adoro Te Fragment 1 21 Temp Smooth 6x Audio 720p S 21 Juli 1924 Mended
sources.description: Interesting footage of the huge sea locks at IJmuiden in the Netherlands in the year 1924. Original title is Adoro-Te.
